<span style="width:100%"><p>FAQs</p></span></div><div data-rid="d50e5784-4548-4ab6-9763-4559d4f8e3c0" class="r-1i94z43" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="a7ecbe5a-1af0-4c37-aeec-2ce634029d09" class="r-8us3o5" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="11b1d53b-7e9e-4eda-a9c8-8df0985fa2c7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R6f32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-dh3y7z"><div data-rid="fb486370-49b4-4da1-92bc-6952d1be9d99" class="r-1glokb4 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How does club identification work without sensors?</p></span></div><div data-rid="0436ff70-b1a6-4b29-8c4e-31f1f05ff4ae" class="r-mk0ljl" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-sd1ter" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R6f32:"><div data-rid="285957b6-257b-4de4-b3b4-7369a9deaea5" class="r-en0ibn"><div data-rid="56893882-c544-4fc2-a885-abc848d5dcf8" class="r-essz2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Every insight Arccos offers — Strokes Gained, scoring breakdowns, and personalized recommendations on where to improve — is available without tagging a single club. For the deepest club-level detail, AI-assisted tagging infers your club based on distance, manual tagging lets you fill in what you want, and Smart Sensors automate it completely. All three are completely optional and never required to get the full Arccos experience.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="c172cf93-de6a-44f4-860e-833ec393f9c3" class="r-mwm979" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="20fb7c04-af08-42a9-97b1-a185bdac699f" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Raf32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-vm42jo"><div data-rid="62df9838-a9db-4c4d-b3b1-9d55d876958a" class="r-1cbjbri alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How is Arccos Air different from Smart Sensors?</p></span></div><div data-rid="bd0a7676-5c62-457d-995a-5062ed9a8b59" class="r-1wz2gzw" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-58vfe9" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Raf32:"><div data-rid="b8d56253-6386-4496-9452-e63d78d156ae" class="r-1bcrxj1"><div data-rid="24d5aeb0-1a1f-456b-b1e3-63095b7c5725" class="r-16qhcsh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Both give you access to the same game tracking features and insights. The difference is how they track. Arccos Air is a single wearable that replaces the need for your phone, Apple Watch, or sensors on your clubs. Smart Sensors attach to each club and require a phone or Apple Watch on the course, but automatically identify which club you hit on every shot. You can also use both together for a fully automatic, phone-free experience.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="bef72456-686a-4fd0-a58d-2b0848da6dcd" class="r-1y0pfpz" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="b2aad086-e326-461b-8086-b3da73f50e06" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Ref32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-7d9uiy"><div data-rid="2fee9eab-342f-4310-98ff-d2b594369897" class="r-1bpy271 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What's in the box?</p></span></div><div data-rid="f55eec68-a625-4908-a1c5-2bd31e4b9076" class="r-1vbn8a" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-krbni4" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Ref32:"><div data-rid="a1d3ae78-93e0-46c4-ab45-23bc527229c3" class="r-1149cgg"><div data-rid="9414718f-2eb7-4b71-9d42-309a4ace5e09" class="r-1e4p2pk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Arccos Air wearable, charging case, and a one-year Game Tracking subscription with full access to the Arccos app. No sensors or additional accessories required.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="5dbc8bda-8778-473d-9060-734e17d21cae" class="r-1em9uj0" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="18cdbc66-fcd0-4b89-b732-33a35a0a1913" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rif32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-x9lf42"><div data-rid="b315119f-0c8d-4ee1-bf29-501b70425b8f" class="r-hhvey9 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How many rounds of data do I need before I get useful insights?</p></span></div><div data-rid="c978df30-46b5-41e1-8fb7-f3cf36ee8992" class="r-1oyz1nv" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1kq46yc" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rif32:"><div data-rid="3ca2ebcf-9a94-435d-8610-b589c3d1ccce" class="r-kyzdzf"><div data-rid="21355c96-c3d8-4fb6-88bd-31afebf16b6b" class="r-augz6e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>One. After your first round you get a complete Strokes Gained breakdown, scoring insights, and Smart Club Distances. The more you play, the sharper your trends and progress tracking become — but you'll have a clear picture of your game from day one.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="4e10f4ac-7a50-4247-a958-6813282e355e" class="r-twgabk" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="746671c5-db04-4e17-9854-bd083f24e3cf" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rmf32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-19ozg7j"><div data-rid="31dcb2fc-7beb-4824-b053-99736fa6c2cc" class="r-2c6hfk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Does Arccos Air work on Android?</p></span></div><div data-rid="cbcfedbe-1a6c-4d1f-b7a2-8ffba7a2a04a" class="r-lv2d9o" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-u28naq" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rmf32:"><div data-rid="c055e05e-2120-41ca-8aed-e2468e61e583" class="r-s8mt25"><div data-rid="c009c61f-7db2-4eb0-b3fe-0cc3423f0fc7" class="r-anueca alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes, sensorless game tracking works on Android with the Arccos Air. AI Strategy and Green Maps are coming soon for Android.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><picture data-rid="672ffd2f-56f5-408c-87f4-ab3d4b947cb2" class="r-1xgyaiw"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/3834fd4a-6f09-4dbd-8cb1-7ada7d72e504?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8